OL,3,CMan who strangled woman he met on
OL,4,Cdating app convicted
OL,6,FA 34-year-old man has been found
OL,7,Fguilty of grave and criminal assault
OL,8,Fand malicious damage after he attacked
OL,9,Fa woman he met on a dating app.
OL,11,FConor James strangled and repeatedly
OL,12,Fhit his victim at her home in Jersey,
OL,13,Fwhile also destroying her mobile phone
OL,14,Fto try and stop her from calling for
OL,15,Fhelp.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/4
