PN,35802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1782730082
OL,3,CMan who strangled woman he met on
OL,4,Cdating app convicted
OL,6,FThe Royal Court heard that, in the
OL,7,Fearly hours of Sunday 16 March 2025,
OL,8,Fthe police were called to St Helier
OL,9,Ftown centre and found the injured
OL,10,Fwoman, who had managed to flee James
OL,11,Fand seek support from members of the
OL,12,Fpublic.
OL,14,FShe had a cut lip, swelling to her
OL,15,Fface and head, marks on her neck, and
OL,16,Fbruising across her body.
OL,18,FJames met the victim on a dating app
OL,19,Fand was invited to her home, but he
OL,20,Fbecame violent after drinking alcohol.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/4
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
