CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1782730082
OL,3,CMan who strangled woman he met on
OL,4,Cdating app convicted
OL,6,FWhen officers arrived at the property,
OL,7,Fthey found blood and other evidence of
OL,8,Fa disturbance.
OL,10,FJames was arrested later that morning
OL,11,Fand subsequently charged.
OL,13,FDetective Constable Bogdan Jagodka
OL,14,Ffrom the States of Jersey Police says:
OL,15,F"This was a serious and sustained
OL,16,Fassault which left the victim with
OL,17,Fsignificant injuries and genuinely
OL,18,Ffearing for her life.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/4
