PN,35804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1782730082
OL,3,CMan who strangled woman he met on
OL,4,Cdating app convicted
OL,6,F"This type of offending reflects the
OL,7,Fharm we continue to see in cases of
OL,8,Fviolence against women and girls, and
OL,9,Fwe are committed to working with
OL,10,Fpartners to prevent abuse, support
OL,11,Fvictims, and bring those responsible
OL,12,Fbefore the courts."
OL,14,FThe officer also praised the victim
OL,15,Ffor her bravery throughout the case.
OL,17,FJames has been taken into custody and
OL,18,Fwill be sentenced at a later date.
